</taxonomicName>
L. (
<bibRefCitation author="Spencer, K. A." box="[607,766,1375,1402]" pageId="26" pageNumber="27" refId="ref74665" refString="Spencer, K. A. (1976) The Agromyzidae (Diptera) of Fennoscandia and Denmark. Part 1. Scandinavian Science Press, Klampenborg, 304 pp." type="book" year="1976">Spencer 1976</bibRefCitation>
